  "chemicalName": "Gamma-linolenic acid (GLA), Linoleic Acid (LA), Arachidonic Acid (AA) / ω-6 fatty acids",
  "description": {
    "en": "Found mostly in plant-based oils including evening primrose oil (EPO), borage oil, and blackcurrant seed oil.",
    "zh-Hant": "奧米加6（學名：Gamma-linolenic acid (GLA), Linoleic Acid (LA), Arachidonic Acid (AA) / ω-6 fatty acids）是一種具有藥用價值的天然產物。現代藥理學研究證實其含有多種生物活性成分，在傳統醫學和現代保健領域均有重要應用價值。",
    "zh-Hans": "奧米加6（学名：Gamma-linolenic acid (GLA), Linoleic Acid (LA), Arachidonic Acid (AA) / ω-6 fatty acids）是一种具有药用價值的天然產物。現代药理学研究证实其含有多种生物活性成分，在传统医学和現代保健領域均有重要应用價值。"
  },
